  "subject": "Cloudevents for DMI Data AVC",
  "commit_message": "Cloudevents for DMI Data AVC\n\n- Introduced cloudevents dependencies and code to publish.\n- Changed v1 to 1.0.0 wherever possible\n- AvcConsumer can consume and forward the cloudevents now\n- Test case refactoring\n- For the time being we will have 2 kafkatemplate until we fully move to\n  cloudevents for all events\n- Need to make a bean as primary to be available by default\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-1719\nChange-Id: Icaa9c5610d4d7d78abdb46edabc8da98c594ce68\nSigned-off-by: mpriyank <priyank.maheshwari@est.tech>\n",
